This is how to sort_array of array:
   Remember that n is array's length
   Do this n times:
      Remember that i is 0
      Do this diff of n and 1 times:
         Remember that j is sum of i and 1
         When item i in array is more than item j in array, then:
            Remember that tmp is item i in array
            Remember that item i in array is item j in array
            Remember that item j in array is tmp
         End when
         Increase i
      End do
   End do
   The answer is array
